PROJECT.NAME: icLapAnag1-mito
PROJECT.TITLE: Laparocerus anagae, mitochondrial assembly, icLapAnag1-mito.
PROJECT.DESCRIPTION: This project collects the mitochondrial assembly of Laparocerus anagae. The assembly is provided by the European Reference Genome Atlas (ERGA, https://www.erga-biodiversity.eu/) via the Biodiversity Genomics Europe project (BGE, https://biodiversitygenomics.eu/).

PROJECT.NAME: icLapAnag1
PROJECT.TITLE: Laparocerus anagae, genome assembly, icLapAnag1, alternate haplotype.
PROJECT.DESCRIPTION: This project provides the genome assembly of Laparocerus anagae. The assembly is provided by the European Reference Genome Atlas (ERGA, https://www.erga-biodiversity.eu/) via the Biodiversity Genomics Europe project (BGE, https://biodiversitygenomics.eu/).
